    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and a limited-slip M-differential that ensures optimal torque distribution. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the drivetrain provides an analog connection lost in modern iterations. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the engine's internal tolerances remain within factory spec. This is a driver-focused example with a solid service history, ready for the twisties.",
