    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a driver-centric 981-generation Cayman S, featuring the high-revving 3.4L DFI flat-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle. This mid-engine platform delivers an optimized polar moment of inertia for surgical turn-in, complemented by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for variable damping. The mechanicals are in excellent order, with recent service records confirming a healthy cooling system and consistent compression across all cylinders. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the optional Porsche Torque Vectoring (PTV) with a mechanical rear differential lock. Minor aesthetic rock chips consistent with spirited use are present, but the drivetrain integrity and communicative steering feel remain uncompromising. A purist\u2019s spec for those prioritizing kinematics and linear throttle response.",
